# artifacts/runs/

Canonical run-output root per [CLAUDE.md §"Implemented infrastructure"](../../CLAUDE.md). Each run lands at `artifacts/runs/{HID}/{run_id}/` with sidecar.json + scientific_payload artifacts.

Per [ADR-0013](../../docs/decisions/ADR-0013-permanent-exploration-no-archive-ninjascript-terminus.md) §4.1 #5, every run output is retained. Protected by §4.3 non-loss-guard.

Files MUST NOT be deleted.
